name: Underworld Contacts
Lore: 'Influence, like any commodity, has a price in the Outer Rim territories.',
Text: 'Deploy on a Tatooine site. Your Force generation here is +1. Opponent may not cancel or modify Force drains at each Tatooine battleground site where you have two aliens with different card titles. At any time, you may use 2 Force to raise your converted Tatooine site to top.',
